Feature: User has no favorite documents
  As a DigiOffice user
  I want to check my favorite documents
  So that I can verify that I have no favorite documents

  Background:
    Given I am a DigiOffice user
    And I have started the DigiOffice mobile application
    And I can see the DigiOffice documents menu

  Scenario: Verify that no favorite documents are listed
    When I navigate to 'My favorite documents'
    Then the 'My favorite documents' view is shown
    And no documents are listed because I have no favorite documents
